%%{init: {'theme':'base','themeVariables':{'fontSize':'16px','primaryColor':'#1e293b','primaryTextColor':'#f1f5f9','primaryBorderColor':'#6366f1','lineColor':'#94a3b8','clusterBkg':'#0f172a','clusterBorder':'#334155'}}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start([Usuario abre MusicFlow]) --> Auth{¿Autenticado?}
    Auth -->|No| Login[Login / Registro<br/>JWT access 15m + refresh 7d]
    Login --> Role
    Auth -->|Sí| Role{Rol}

    Role -->|ADMIN| Admin[Panel Admin<br/>gestión usuarios · stats IA]
    Role -->|CLIENT| Home[Inicio Cliente]

    subgraph Plataformas
        direction LR
        Web[Web / Desktop<br/>React + Electron]
        Mobile[Móvil<br/>Flutter]
    end
    Home --> Plataformas

    Plataformas --> Library[📚 Biblioteca<br/>subir / gestionar tracks · playlists]
    Library --> Player[▶️ Reproductor<br/>Web Audio API / just_audio]

    Player --> EQ[🎚️ Ecualización multinivel]
    EQ --> EQG[Global]
    EQ --> EQP[Playlist]
    EQ --> EQT[Track]
    EQ --> EQS[Segmento temporal<br/>intro · verso · coro]

    Player --> AI[🤖 Agente IA<br/>sugiere EQ en lenguaje natural]
    AI -->|propone config| EQS
    Player --> Analytics[📊 Analytics<br/>historial · stats de escucha]

    Library -. offline/online .-> Sync[🔄 Sync híbrido]
    EQ -. cambios .-> Sync
    Sync -->|pull / push| API

    Admin --> API
    Plataformas --> API[(Backend NestJS API<br/>auth · library · equalizer<br/>ai-agent · analytics · sync · admin)]

    API --> Prisma[Prisma ORM]
    Prisma --> DB[(PostgreSQL<br/>13 tablas)]
    API --> Redis[(Redis + BullMQ)]
    Redis --> Worker[Worker nocturno<br/>agrega ListeningStats]
    Worker --> DB
    AI --> Claude[Claude API]
    API --> Mail[Mailer<br/>reset contraseña]

    classDef store fill:#312e81,stroke:#6366f1,color:#e0e7ff;
    classDef feature fill:#155e75,stroke:#22d3ee,color:#cffafe;
    class DB,Redis,API store;
    class Library,Player,EQ,AI,Analytics,Sync feature;
